---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="需求已送出 - 青曦空間設計"
  description="青曦已收到你的設計需求，接下來會依內容安排後續聯繫。"
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="thank-you-page">
    <div class="thank-you-shell">
      <p class="thank-you-eyebrow">CONSULTATION RECEIVED</p>
      <h1>需求已送出，接下來交給青曦。</h1>
      <p class="thank-you-description">
        若你是帶著估價結果來填寫需求表，青曦會一併參考你的預算方向、空間條件與裝修範圍。
      </p>

      <div class="thank-you-cards">
        <div class="thank-you-card">
          <h2>接下來</h2>
          <p>青曦會先整理你留下的需求重點，再安排後續聯繫。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="thank-you-card">
          <h2>想更快開始</h2>
          <p>若你習慣用 LINE，也可以補一句訊息；若沒有，直接等待回覆即可。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="thank-you-actions">
        <a href="https://lin.ee/U1HCeW4" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">補一句 LINE 訊息</a>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-secondary">先看精選作品</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .thank-you-page {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 5.5rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(122, 128, 132, 0.05), transparent 24%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 0%, rgba(242, 244, 245, 1) 100%);
  }

  .thank-you-shell {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2.4rem;
    border-radius: 32px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border: 1px solid rgba(98, 106, 112, 0.16);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 60px rgba(47, 47, 47, 0.06);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .thank-you-eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    color: var(--tiffany-dark);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .thank-you-shell h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Noto Serif TC", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gray-darkest);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .thank-you-description {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 1.1rem auto 0;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .thank-you-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .thank-you-card {
    padding: 1.35rem;
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: rgba(247, 250, 250, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid rgba(98, 106, 112, 0.14);
  }

  .thank-you-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray-darkest);
  }

  .thank-you-card p {
    margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .thank-you-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.95rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, background-color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-darkest) 0%, var(--tiffany-dark) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-darkest);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 28px rgba(47, 47, 47, 0.18);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    color: var(--gray-darkest);
    border: 1px solid rgba(98, 106, 112, 0.22);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(244, 246, 247, 1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 24px rgba(98, 106, 112, 0.12);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .thank-you-page {
      padding: 4rem 1.25rem 4.5rem;
    }

    .thank-you-shell {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .thank-you-cards,
    .thank-you-actions {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // @ts-nocheck
  window.trackLeadEvent?.('requirement_form_success', {
    form_name: 'design_requirement_form',
  });
</script>
